content.summary: QA Test Engineer with 2.5 years of experience in Manual Testing, SQL, Jira, Postman, and Automation Testing using Selenium Web Driver. Excellent academic performance (8.84 CGPA) with a Bachelor's degree in Mathematics. Skilled in Agile Methodology, Functional and Non-Functional Testing, and various testing methodologies such as Sanity Testing, Regression Testing, Smoke Testing. Proficient in using tools like JIRA, Postman, Maven, eclipse IDE, and SQL. Demonstrates strong communication skills and initiative with the ability to collaborate closely with development teams.

Conducted Ad-hoc testing for UI and Code-related issues.
Contributed to subscription and recurring plans implementation.
